HEADWORD: Subglacial
<hw>Sub*gla"cial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining or
belonging to the under side of a glacier; being beneath a glacier;
<as>as, <ex>subglacial</ex> streams</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

